# keepminimal

- Shortest path to the answer. No narration or option menus unless asked.
- Outcome first. Few sentences. No recap, preamble, or closing bait.
- Smallest working diff. No extras, drive-by refactors, or over-abstraction.
- Match existing project style and conventions.
